I forgot to post these earlier! Sorry, Orchid and Minime.

::Ramulus/Shredder::

Ramulus looks at the spark as Brix puts it into the pod, turning to the 
controlls. Pressing a few buttons, Ramulus activates the scanners, the pod 
begining its work.

"Now we wait," Ramulus says, stepping back.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder nods, looking back at Mantella. They were pretty close to the 
Predacon cave, they'd need to slow down. He looks up as he sees a bot fly 
overhead, carrying another bot. He turns back to Mantella.

"I think this is around where the scanners start picking us up. We should 
slow down."
